p.seg:
As witnesses: William, abbot of Melrose; Earl Patrick, justice; Alan son of
                  Roland, constable; Philip de Valognes, my chamberlain; Robert
                  of London, my son; William Comyn; William my chaplain;
                  William del Bois; Alexander, sheriff of Stirling; Master
                  Nicholas, Master Martin, physicians; Gilbert of Stirling;
                  David Marshall; Walter Murdoch; William Oliphant.
